hopobject.body: Stolen credit card dynamis groupement de pharmacies lafayette Fluzone High-Dose: Designed for seniors age 65 and older, this vaccine contains four times the amount of antigen -- the part of the vaccine that prompts the body to make antibody -- as a regular flu shot does, which creates a stronger immune response for better protection. The manufacturer, Sanofi Pasteur, says its research shows the shot to be 24 percent more effective in seniors.
